msgid "Previewing the Animation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/rendering_the_animation.rst:13
msgid ""
"Animations can be previewed directly in the Toonz work area, including in"
" the preview mode all the flipbook features, or by rendering a preview "
"and visualizing it in a separate flipbook window."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/rendering_the_animation.rst:15
msgid ""
