msgid ""
"If the computer performance worsens during the preview process of raster "
"animation levels, try activating the Minimize Raster Image Fragmentation "
"option in the Preferences > General dialog (see  :ref:`Optimizing the "
"Memory Usage <optimizing_the_memory_usage>`  )."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/rendering_the_animation.rst:22
msgid "Previewing Frames in the Viewer"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/rendering_the_animation.rst:23
msgid ""
